column31: If Kevin beats Piper in 2025 standings = 2026 1st round pick from Kevin
If Kevin beats Piper in 2025 standings = 2026 1st round pick to Kevin

If  Kevin beats Piper in 2025 standings & Piper beats Kevin in 2027 standings = 2028 1st from Kevin
If Kevin beats Piper in both 2025 & 2027 standings = 2029 2nd round pick to Kevin
If Piper beats JP in 2027 standings = 2028 2nd round pick to JP
If Piper beats JP in 2027 standings = 2028 1st round pick from JP
